        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Organize subscriptions by category and see exactly where your money is going each month.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Metrics Mockup -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm p-4 overflow-hidden aspect-square flex flex-col">
        <div class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-slate-500 mb-3">Monthly Spend · 2024</div>
        <div class="flex items-end gap-1.5 flex-1">
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center gap-1">
            <div class="w-full bg-indigo-200 rounded-t-sm h-8"></div>
            <span class="text-[8px] text-slate-400">O</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center gap-1">
            <div class="w-full bg-indigo-300 rounded-t-sm h-11"></div>
            <span class="text-[8px] text-slate-400">N</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center gap-1">
            <div class="w-full bg-indigo-400 rounded-t-sm h-14"></div>
            <span class="text-[8px] text-slate-400">D</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center gap-1">
            <div class="w-full bg-indigo-500 rounded-t-sm h-12"></div>
            <span class="text-[8px] text-slate-400">E</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center gap-1">
            <div class="w-full bg-indigo-600 rounded-t-sm h-16"></div>
            <span class="text-[8px] text-slate-400">F</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center gap-1">
            <div class="w-full bg-indigo-700 rounded-t-sm h-14"></div>
            <span class="text-[8px] text-slate-400">M</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-2 pt-2 border-t border-slate-100 flex justify-between text-[9px]">
          <span class="text-slate-400">Avg <span class="font-mono font-semibold text-slate-600">$87.32</span></span>
          <span class="text-emerald-500 font-semibold">↓ 12%</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Testimonials -->
<section class="py-20 px-4 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tighter text-center mb-12">
      People who stopped wasting money
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <blockquote class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm p-6">
        <div class="text-amber-400 text-sm mb-3">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">"Subscriptify simplified the management and visualization of all my subscriptions. With their notifications I was able to unsubscribe from services I no longer used."</p>
        <footer class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="h-8 w-8 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold text-indigo-700">JD</div>
